---
import Container from "../Container.astro";
import Section from "../Section.astro";
---

<Section>

  <Container>

    <div class="story-grid">

      <div class="heading">

        <p class="eyebrow">OUR STORY</p>

        <h2>
          Nearly three decades of manufacturing built on trust.
        </h2>

      </div>

      <div class="content">

        <p>
          S R Group is a family-owned chemical manufacturing group based in
          Chhatral GIDC, Gujarat.
        </p>

        <p>
          Established in 1997 by the late Shri Ramanbhai Patel together with
          his sons, Nilesh Patel and Krushi Patel, the company was founded with
          a clear vision — to build a business rooted in integrity, dependable
          products, and lasting customer relationships.
        </p>

        <p>
          Over the years, S R Group has grown into three manufacturing
          companies — S R Industries, S R Plast, and S R Polymers —
          manufacturing industrial chemicals, distilled solvents, and
          unsaturated polyester resins for customers across India while
          steadily expanding into international markets.
        </p>

        <p>
          With a strong foundation built over nearly three decades,
          Henil Patel and Kushal Patel represent the next generation of
          S R Group, carrying forward its legacy by combining the company's
          core values with a modern approach to manufacturing and innovation.
        </p>

        <p>
          As the business continues to evolve, the principles on which it was
          founded remain unchanged.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </Container>

</Section>

<style>

.story-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1.5fr;
gap:6rem;
align-items:start;
}

.heading{
position:sticky;
top:120px;
}

.eyebrow{
font-size:.85rem;
font-weight:600;
letter-spacing:.15em;
text-transform:uppercase;
color:var(--color-accent);
margin-bottom:1rem;
}

.heading h2{
max-width:360px;
}

.content{
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
gap:2rem;
}

.content p{
font-size:1.1rem;
line-height:1.9;
color:var(--color-text-light);
margin:0;
}

@media (max-width:900px){

.story-grid{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
gap:3rem;
}

.heading{
position:static;
}

.heading h2{
max-width:none;
}

}

</style>
